I just need a piece of Ji Su.

12
00:01:06,069 --> 00:01:07,870
It was nothing.

13
00:01:08,939 --> 00:01:11,480
It was someone I met
for the first time,

14
00:01:13,140 --> 00:01:16,549
but he just dug into my heart.

15
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:42,209
(Kim Ji Su)

16
00:01:49,650 --> 00:01:51,319
(Kim Ji Su)

17
00:01:55,250 --> 00:01:56,750
Why did you do that?

18
00:01:57,790 --> 00:01:59,120
I'm sorry,

19
00:01:59,260 --> 00:02:02,730
but I heard you two
were long-time friends.

20
00:02:02,730 --> 00:02:04,060
Friends?

21
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:07,700
As if you know anything about us.

22
00:02:07,700 --> 00:02:09,129
I just...

23
00:02:09,129 --> 00:02:10,569
Did Ha Won put you up to this?

24
00:02:10,569 --> 00:02:13,639
I don't know.
I honestly don't know who he is.

25
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:15,370
I...

26
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:19,009
All I wanted was to do you a favor.

27
00:02:19,009 --> 00:02:22,210
Do you know what
his last words to me were?

28
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:27,120
"Call me when
your life becomes miserable."

29
00:02:29,250 --> 00:02:30,889
Misery found me...

30
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:33,060
but I never contacted him.

31
00:02:33,889 --> 00:02:36,689
I won't ever. Do you know why?

32
00:02:36,689 --> 00:02:37,860
It's because...

33
